<title>MEXICO: RESEARCH ALERT - Autrey upgraded.</title>
<headline>RESEARCH ALERT - Autrey upgraded.</headline>
<dateline>MEXICO CITY 1997-03-07</dateline>
<text>
<p>Robert Fleming brokerage on Friday raised its rating on Casa Autrey to long term buy from hold.</p>
<p>The brokerage said in a report the company's fourth quarter results were below market expectations.</p>
<p>&quot;We believe the fact that the stock is now out of favor, just as consumer demand is showing signs of life, offers a good entry point,&quot; the report said.</p>
<p>The company's Mexico shares fell 0.60 peso at the close of trading Friday to 14.40 pesos. American Depositary Receipts closed at 18, down 5/8.</p>
<p>((--Timna Tanners, Mexico City newsroom +525 728-7903)).</p>
